Package itcom.cartographer.Database

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ProgressInputStream.Listener  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Database
    SQLite Database to store all location data that the app needs
    FavPlace
    An object that represents a favourite place
    FavPlaceResult
    An object that represents a favourite place result (looked up on Google Maps)
    LocationHistoryObject
    An object that represents an entry in the location history file from Google.
    ProcessJSON
    An activity that processes a location history file from Google and put in a database while showing a loading screen to the user
    ProgressInputStream
    A special InputStream that estimates the progress of how much of the file has been read Source: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/27890287/how-to-publish-progress-for-large-json-file-parsing-with-gson
